hgview intallation notes
========================


This is still a development version but already useable

It is very simple to use and install from the hg repository :

hg clone http://www.logilab.org/hgview

cd <ANY_HG_REPO>
python $PATH_TO_HGVIEW_DIR/hgview.py


There's already a TODO list of features that I wish to implement
in TODO.txt.


